  <p>Consider the following results for the number of words per minute by each participant.</p>
  
  <exercise xml:id="inv4-8-d" label="I4.8.4">
    <title>Examine Distributions</title>
    <statement>
      <p>Do you see much of a difference between the two distributions? What is the observed difference in the sample means? Do you think this difference in sample means will be statistically significant? Explain.</p>
    </statement>
