      <statement>
        <p>A farmer wants to see whether referring to cows by name increases their milk production. He selects half of his cows at random, gives them names, and frequently calls them by name. The other half of his cows he does not call by name. Then he measured the milk production of each cow over one week.</p>
      </statement>
      <response/>
